  "prompt": "What is Instagram's hourly comment limit?",
  "response": "Instagram does not publicly disclose the exact hourly comment limit, as it may vary based on several factors, including account age, activity, and overall engagement. However, the general guideline is that Instagram allows users to post around 30-60 comments per hour. \n\nTo avoid any potential restrictions or account penalties, it's recommended to stay within these limits and not engage in spammy behavior. If you exceed these limits, your account may be temporarily blocked from commenting, or in severe cases, permanently banned. \n\nKeep in mind that these limits are subject to change, and Instagram may adjust them without prior notice. Always use the platform responsibly and respect its terms of service.",
